originalText.text: We are delighted with the design for our extension that Studio Morsa has produced. From day one we were impressed with their approach and the communication and responsiveness to our requests have been first-class, despite this being such a challenging time. Thoroughly recommended.

I would never give them any business.I experienced one of the lowest levels of competence, accountability, trust!!
The building department recorded two violations, on the plans of an addition of my house.
When I asked Mr.Morello why did this happened, he blamed me for allowing the DOB inspector to inspect the job!!
I had to hire another architect, to fix the damage done.
